title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 18: THE WOKE PRINCE STEVE LEE
description:
Thanks for tuning into another fun and exciting episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode, Ryan and I, welcome from Mangchi, Steve Lee. On this episode we discuss...
1) Stevee Weebee and Mangchi
2) David Icke
3) The Freemasons
4) Lizard People
5) Interdimensional Travel
6) Invisible Prisons
7) Blood Sacrifices
If you want to help the show grow please rate and review on iTunes, tweet and retweet! IF you're on reddit, please post the show on some the conspiracy subreddit or start a Tin Foil Hat subreddit. The bigger the show gets the better the guest we can get. Thank you for all of your love and support!
